#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1441
msgid ""
"Uses a front-end AJAX endpoint instead of admin-ajax.php to reduce overhead. "
"Default: Off. Impact on Speed: Medium."
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1450
msgid "Load Only Post ID"
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1454
msgid ""
"Loads only post IDs. Best for ID-based widgets but may break those needing "
"full post details. Default: Off. Impact on Speed: High."
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1463
msgid "Skip Pagination Count"
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1467
msgid ""
"Do NOT enable this if you are using pagination. Skips counting total posts. "
"Default: Off. Impact on Speed: Medium."
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1476
msgid "Bypass Query Modifications"
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1480
msgid ""
"Do NOT enable this if you are using a translation plugin (WPML, Polylang, "
"TranslatePress, etc.). Ignores query tweaks. Default: Off. Impact on Speed: "
"Medium."
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1489
#: widgets/class-bpfwe-post-widget.php:149
msgid "Posts Per Page"
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1491
msgid ""
"Limits the number of posts per page. Use -1 to use post widget’s default "
"value, if accesible by the query. Default: -1. Impact on Speed: High."
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1501
msgid "Cache filter’s terms (s)"
msgstr ""

#: widgets/class-bpfwe-filter-widget.php:1503
msgid ""
"Caches filter terms for faster loading. Set to 0 to disable (not "
"recommended). Default: 86400 (1 day). Impact on Speed: High."
